.TH SHOAL-HISTORY 1 "July 2026" "Shoal 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
shoal-history \- query and maintain the Shoal journal
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B shoal-history
.RI [ \-\-state-dir " path" ]
.RI [ \-\-json ]
.I command
.RI [ options ]
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B query
Filter journal entries.
.TP
.B show
Show one entry.
.TP
.BR pin , unpin
Manage retained CAS objects.
.TP
.B gc
Preview or apply storage collection.
.TP
.B status
Report database and CAS use.
.TP
.B undo
Apply recorded inverse operations.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR shoal (1)
